N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 31.3 - Violations

State Regulations
A violation of the provisions of this Part shall be cause
for the revocation, cancellation or suspension of the license of the
manufacturer or wholesaler participating or concerned in such
violation. Notes
